{"tid":639953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大排華開始？客貨車撞人地點為華人聚腳點 25死傷包括多名華人","createTime":"2018-04-24T02:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T03:39:35.000Z","uid":65346,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"34bc6b0ddbb754c8468d07faa9334e05e8e30063","tid":639953,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T02:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180424/58110132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F58110132&d=4zss2oqrg8H8V9J5SRC0ECwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f58c0340\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F58110132&h=5235d56c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180424/58110132</a><br />\n<br />\n【10:00 更新】<br />\n● 現場為華人聚腳點 當局證實有華人死傷<br />\n<br />\n加拿大多倫多周一發生疑似恐怖襲擊，東北部市郊一個繁忙路口有客貨車鏟上行人路，撞倒多名途人。警方表示，事件造成10死15傷。美國消息人士指，事件很可能是恐襲。<br />\n警方表示，租來的白色客貨車，當地下午約1時30分，剷上央街（Yonge Street）與芬奇大道（Finch Avenue）交界的行人路，並撞倒途人，司機之後試圖開車逃去，在幾條街外被警方拘捕。<br />\n警方證實司機是25歲的米納西安（Alek Minassian）。傳媒引述政府官員消息，指他與恐怖組織無關。警方未有交代傷者傷勢，亦未知事發原因。Sunnybrook醫院表示接收了7名傷者，當中5人危殆，2人傷勢嚴重。<br />\n警方封鎖附近街道調查，附近地鐵服務暫停。目擊者指，貨車剷上行人路後以高速行駛，是蓄意撞人。"},{"pid":"f02bd52d16080d3fdbf5c9d8db5215aaf4f6419e","tid":639953,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T02:14:59.000Z","msg":"Toronto 邊樹都多華人<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"727bd105b2499ab5281543607d1e42f69863334b","tid":639953,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"North York最多係韓國人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84abdc7de546b827deab8986525ae565295b78d2","tid":639953,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:05:18.000Z","msg":"留名等睇Trudeau又發咩膠論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d828fd2518118a6ab08fccfdc49f5272e2a1ff26","tid":639953,"uid":182519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"我今日同班friend係附近，唔關排華事，成個Toronto都多中國人，係排華就去Richmond Hill,基本上只有中國人，搵個鬼佬都難"},{"pid":"60918b9df565ac57ce6abb6680d2a02e1d1016c6","tid":639953,"uid":57844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:13:08.000Z","msg":"咁都叫排華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔係咪打飛機打到痴左線"},{"pid":"80cb69c0d07a47c127ff6806ffece0434e781665","tid":639953,"uid":182519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"60918b9df565ac57ce6abb6680d2a02e1d1016c6","tid":639953,"uid":57844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:13:08.000Z","msg":"咁都叫排華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔係咪打飛機打到痴左線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:16:55.000Z","msg":"見到有華人在內就話排華，真係on9"},{"pid":"1f5cf75d3f01195e6622b54221b4d03557934d49","tid":639953,"uid":65346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"80cb69c0d07a47c127ff6806ffece0434e781665","tid":639953,"uid":182519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"60918b9df565ac57ce6abb6680d2a02e1d1016c6","tid":639953,"uid":57844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:13:08.000Z","msg":"咁都叫排華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔係咪打飛機打到痴左線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:16:55.000Z","msg":"見到有華人在內就話排華，真係on9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:19:30.000Z","msg":"陸續有來。。。。<br />\n打中興單野。。。已經好有八國聯軍  feel<br